        <span class="section-label">The Show</span>
        <h2 class="about-heading">Not Just Fights.<br />An Experience.</h2>
        <p class="about-lead">Since 2019, 247 Fighting Championships has been building something different in Pittsburgh combat sports. We run our own venue. We have our own streaming platform. We put on a show that goes beyond the cage.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="focus-cards">
        <div class="focus-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="focus-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold-bright)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>For the Fans</h3>
          <p>Our fans come first. Every event is built to give you the thrill of live combat, whether you're in the front row or streaming from home. This is about bringing you closer to the action.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="focus-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold-bright)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>For Fighters + Gyms</h3>
          <p>Our fighters and the gyms that train them are the backbone of what we do. We invest in creating opportunities for up-and-coming talent and seasoned fighters to showcase their skills.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="focus-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold-bright)" stroke-width="1.5"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </div>
